&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;:set syntax on&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will trun syntac highlighting on&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;:set number&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will show the line number&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;:hardcopy &amp;gt; file.pdf&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will write the file to the pdf file.pdf&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;:set printooptions=right:20pc,left:20pc,top:20pc,bottom:20pc&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will appy margin to the print output based on the given parameters&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;set autoindent&lt;/tt&gt;
&lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;filetype plugin indent on&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will autoindents the code as we type&lt;/p&gt;
